name: 5th International Conference on Digital Health
content: With great pleasure we welcome you as a Speaker/Delegate at "5th International Conference on Digital Health” which is slated to be held during May 25-26, 2023 at Singapore City, Singapore. The conference deliberations would be on the theme: "Redefining Innovation in Healthcare by Modern Technologies". Our audience will definitely look forward to learning from your presentation. So, we are feeling privileged to welcome you as a speaker to our conference.
